Mass 211: Temporal Validation

dat.train <- mcalls.full %>%
    filter(
      cat.code != 'RP-1500.1400-500',
      cat.code != 'RP-1500.1400-800',
      date >= ymd('2016-06-01'),
      date < ymd('2017-01-01')
    ) %>% CleanDataForRF()

dat.test <- mcalls.full %>%
    filter(
      cat.code != 'RP-1500.1400-500',
      cat.code != 'RP-1500.1400-800',
      date >= ymd('2017-01-01'),
      date < ymd('2017-09-01')
    ) %>% CleanDataForRF()

set.seed(1984)
RFXY <- function(dat) {
  y <- dat$calls
  x <- dat %>% select(-calls)
  # removed mostly-zero variables and strongly correlated variables
  # x2 <- x[, -nearZeroVar(x)]
  # x2 <- x2[, -findCorrelation(cor(x2), .9)]
  list(x=x, y=y)
}
xy.train <- RFXY(dat.train)
xy.test <- RFXY(dat.test)
model <- randomForest(
  xy.train$x, xy.train$y,
  xy.test$x, xy.test$y,
  # na.action = na.roughfix,
  # subset = train,
  ntree = 400,
  mtry = 20,
  importance = TRUE)
model

plot(model, main="Random Forest applied to 2-1-1 demand prediction")

library(pscl)

dat2.train <- mcalls.full %>%
    filter(
      cat.code != 'RP-1500.1400-500',
      cat.code != 'RP-1500.1400-800',
      date >= ymd('2016-06-01'),
      date < ymd('2017-01-01')
    ) %>%
    DistinctCalls() %>%
    GeoCount("zip", TRUE) %>%
    filter(
      TotalPop > 200,
      n_call >= 5
    )

dat2.test <- mcalls.full %>%
    filter(
      cat.code != 'RP-1500.1400-500',
      cat.code != 'RP-1500.1400-800',
      date >= ymd('2017-01-01'),
      date < ymd('2017-09-01')
    ) %>%
    DistinctCalls() %>%
    GeoCount("zip", TRUE) %>%
    filter(
      TotalPop > 200,
      n_call >= 5
    )
rfe_sizes <- c(2, 4, 8, 10, 13, 15, 20, 25, 30, 40)

                   # resampling methods: bootstrap
                   method = "boot",
                   number = 550,
                   verbose = FALSE)
lmProfile <- rfe(xy.train$x, xy.train$y, sizes = rfe_sizes, rfeControl = ctrl)
